  entries:
  - id: heart
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: concept
    title: Kalp
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Heart_External
    tags: heart; organ; pump; circulation
    body: Kalp
    steps: " dola\u015F\u0131m sisteminin temel organ\u0131d\u0131r ve kas\u0131l\u0131p
      gev\u015Feyerek kan\u0131n v\xFCcutta dola\u015Fmas\u0131n\u0131 sa\u011Flar."
    source: "[\"Kalp kas\u0131lma ve gev\u015Feme hareketleri ile kan\u0131 pompalar.\",
      \"Akci\u011Ferlerden gelen oksijen bak\u0131m\u0131ndan zengin kan\u0131 dokulara
      g\xF6nderir.\", \"Dokulardan d\xF6nen oksijen oran\u0131 d\xFC\u015F\xFCk kan\u0131
      akci\u011Ferlere y\xF6nlendirir.\", \"Kan\u0131n damarlar i\xE7erisindeki dola\u015F\u0131m\u0131
      kalbin pompalama i\u015Flevine ba\u011Fl\u0131d\u0131r.\", \"Kalbin duvar\u0131
      \xFC\xE7 tabakadan olu\u015Fur: endokard, miyokard ve epikard.\", \"Perikard
      visseral ve paryetal olmak \xFCzere iki katl\u0131d\u0131r.\", \"Perikard katmanlar\u0131
      aras\u0131ndaki s\u0131v\u0131 kalbin hareketini kolayla\u015Ft\u0131r\u0131r
      ve s\xFCrt\xFCnmeyi azalt\u0131r.\"]"
  - id: basis_cordis
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: structure
    title: Basis cordis
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Heart_External
    tags: heart; external; base; basis_cordis; location
    body: "Kalbin taban\u0131 (basis cordis) \xFCst tarafta yer al\u0131r."
    steps: 
    source: "Ders kitab\u0131 s.131"
  - id: apex_cordis
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: structure
    title: Apex cordis
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Heart_External
    tags: heart; external; apex; apex_cordis; location
    body: "Kalbin tepesi (apex cordis) alt tarafta yer al\u0131r."
    steps: 
    source: "Ders kitab\u0131 s.131"
  - id: heart_chambers
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: concept
    title: "Kalbin odac\u0131klar\u0131"
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Heart_Internal
    tags: heart; chambers; atrium; ventricle; anatomy
    body: "Kalbin yap\u0131s\u0131nda d\xF6rt odac\u0131k bulunur."
    steps: "[\"\xDCst k\u0131s\u0131mda iki kulak\xE7\u0131k (atrium), alt k\u0131s\u0131mda
      iki kar\u0131nc\u0131k (ventriculus) yer al\u0131r.\", \"Kalbin sa\u011F taraf\u0131nda
      sa\u011F kulak\xE7\u0131k (atrium dexter) ve sa\u011F kar\u0131nc\u0131k (ventriculus
      dexter), sol taraf\u0131nda ise sol kulak\xE7\u0131k (atrium sinister) ve sol
      kar\u0131nc\u0131k (ventriculus sinister) bulunur.\" , \"Kulak\xE7\u0131klar\u0131
      birbirinden ay\u0131ran b\xF6lmeye septum interatriale, kar\u0131nc\u0131klar\u0131
      ay\u0131ran b\xF6lmeye ise septum interventrikulare denir.\" , \"Bu b\xF6lmeler
      sayesinde kalbin sa\u011F taraf\u0131ndaki kirli kan ile sol taraf\u0131ndaki
      temiz kan birbirine kar\u0131\u015Fmaz.\"]"
    source: "Ders kitab\u0131 s.131"
  - id: atrium_dexter
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: structure
    title: Atrium dexter
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Heart_Internal
    tags: heart; internal; atrium; right
    body: "Atrium dexter (sa\u011F kulak\xE7\u0131k) kalbin sa\u011F \xFCst odac\u0131\u011F\u0131d\u0131r."
    steps: "[\"\xDCst ana toplardamar ve alt ana toplardamar arac\u0131l\u0131\u011F\u0131yla
      v\xFCcuttan gelen oksijeni azalm\u0131\u015F kan burada toplan\u0131r.\" ,
      \"Sa\u011F kulak\xE7\u0131k bu kan\u0131 trik\xFCspit kapaktan ge\xE7irerek
      sa\u011F kar\u0131nc\u0131\u011Fa g\xF6nderir.\"]"
    source: "Ders kitab\u0131 s.131"
  - id: atrium_sinister
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: structure
    title: Atrium sinister
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Heart_Internal
    tags: heart; internal; atrium; left
    body: "Atrium sinister (sol kulak\xE7\u0131k) kalbin sol \xFCst odac\u0131\u011F\u0131d\u0131r."
    steps: "[\"Akci\u011Ferlerden oksijen bak\u0131m\u0131ndan zengin kan akci\u011Fer
      toplardamarlar\u0131 arac\u0131l\u0131\u011F\u0131yla buraya gelir.\"  , \"Sol
      kulak\xE7\u0131k bu kan\u0131 mitral kapaktan ge\xE7irerek sol kar\u0131nc\u0131\u011Fa
      iletir.\"]"
    source: "Ders kitab\u0131 s.131"
  - id: ventriculus_dexter
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: structure
    title: Ventriculus dexter
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Heart_Internal
    tags: heart; internal; ventricle; right
    body: "Ventriculus dexter (sa\u011F kar\u0131nc\u0131k) kalbin sa\u011F alt odac\u0131\u011F\u0131d\u0131r."
    steps: "[\"Sa\u011F kulak\xE7\u0131ktan gelen oksijeni azalm\u0131\u015F kan\u0131
      akci\u011Ferlere g\xF6nderir.\" , \"Bu kan akci\u011Fer atardamar\u0131 arac\u0131l\u0131\u011F\u0131yla
      akci\u011Ferlere ta\u015F\u0131n\u0131r ve burada oksijenlenir.\"]"
    source: "Ders kitab\u0131 s.131"
  - id: ventriculus_sinister
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: structure
    title: Ventriculus sinister
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Heart_Internal
    tags: heart; internal; ventricle; left
    body: "Ventriculus sinister (sol kar\u0131nc\u0131k) kalbin en g\xFC\xE7l\xFC
      kas yap\u0131s\u0131na sahip odac\u0131\u011F\u0131d\u0131r."
    steps: "[\"Sol kulak\xE7\u0131ktan gelen oksijen bak\u0131m\u0131ndan zengin
      kan\u0131 aort arac\u0131l\u0131\u011F\u0131yla t\xFCm v\xFCcuda pompalar.\"]"
    source: "Ders kitab\u0131 s.131"
  - id: vena_cava_superior
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: vessel
    title: "\xDCst ana toplardamar"
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Heart_External
    tags: heart; vessel; vein
    body: "\xDCst ana toplardamar"
    steps: " ba\u015F ve \xFCst v\xFCcut b\xF6lgelerinden gelen oksijeni azalm\u0131\u015F
      kan\u0131 kalbin sa\u011F kulak\xE7\u0131\u011F\u0131na ta\u015F\u0131yan b\xFCy\xFCk
      toplardamard\u0131r."
    source: 
  - id: vena_cava_inferior
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: vessel
    title: Alt ana toplardamar
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Heart_External
    tags: heart; vessel; vein
    body: Alt ana toplardamar
    steps: " v\xFCcudun alt b\xF6lgelerinden gelen oksijeni azalm\u0131\u015F kan\u0131
      kalbin sa\u011F kulak\xE7\u0131\u011F\u0131na ta\u015F\u0131yan b\xFCy\xFCk
      toplardamard\u0131r."
    source: 
  - id: aorta
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: vessel
    title: Aort
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Heart_External
    tags: heart; vessel; artery; aorta
    body: Aort
    steps: " kalpten \xE7\u0131kan en b\xFCy\xFCk atardamard\u0131r."
    source: "[\"Sol kar\u0131nc\u0131ktan \xE7\u0131kan oksijen bak\u0131m\u0131ndan
      zengin kan\u0131 t\xFCm v\xFCcuda ta\u015F\u0131r.\" , \"Aort, sistemik dola\u015F\u0131m\u0131n
      ba\u015Flang\u0131\xE7 damar\u0131d\u0131r.\"]"
  - id: pulmonary_vein
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: vessel
    title: "Akci\u011Fer toplardamar\u0131"
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Heart_External
    tags: heart; vessel; vein; pulmonary
    body: "Akci\u011Fer toplardamar\u0131"
    steps: " akci\u011Ferlerde oksijenlenen kan\u0131 kalbin sol kulak\xE7\u0131\u011F\u0131na
      ta\u015F\u0131yan damard\u0131r."
    source: "[\"Akci\u011Ferlerden gelen oksijen bak\u0131m\u0131ndan zengin kan\u0131
      kalbe getirir.\", \"Di\u011Fer toplardamarlardan farkl\u0131 olarak oksijen
      bak\u0131m\u0131ndan zengin kan ta\u015F\u0131r.\"]"
  - id: heart_valves
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: structure
    title: "Kalbin kapaklar\u0131"
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Heart_Internal
    tags: heart; valve; mitral; tricuspid; aortic; pulmonary
    body: "Kalpte d\xF6rt adet kapak bulunur."
    steps: "[\"Bu kapaklar\u0131n ikisi atriyoventrik\xFCler kapaklar, ikisi ise
      semilunar kapaklard\u0131r.\" , \"Atriyoventrik\xFCler kapaklar, kulak\xE7\u0131klar
      ile kar\u0131nc\u0131klar aras\u0131nda yer al\u0131r ve mitral kapak ile trik\xFCspit
      kapaktan olu\u015Fur.\" , \"Semilunar kapaklar ise kar\u0131nc\u0131klar ile
      b\xFCy\xFCk atardamarlar aras\u0131nda bulunur ve aort kapa\u011F\u0131 ile
      pulmoner kapaktan olu\u015Fur.\", \"Kalp kapaklar\u0131, kalbin kas\u0131lmas\u0131
      ve gev\u015Femesi s\u0131ras\u0131nda kan\u0131n geriye do\u011Fru akmas\u0131n\u0131
      engelleyerek kan\u0131n tek y\xF6nl\xFC ilerlemesini sa\u011Flar.\"]"
    source: "Ders kitab\u0131 s.132"
  - id: coronary_arteries
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: concept
    title: Koroner arterler
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Heart_External
    tags: heart; coronary; artery; circulation
    body: "Kalp kas\u0131na oksijen bak\u0131m\u0131ndan zengin kan ta\u015F\u0131yan
      damarlara koroner arterler denir."
    steps: "[\"Koroner arterler aorttan ayr\u0131lan ilk dallard\u0131r.\" , \"Sa\u011F
      koroner arter kalbin sa\u011F taraf\u0131n\u0131, sol koroner arter ise kalbin
      sol taraf\u0131n\u0131 besler.\" , \"Bu damarlarda olu\u015Fan daralma veya
      t\u0131kan\u0131kl\u0131klar kalp kas\u0131n\u0131n yeterince beslenmesini
      engelleyebilir ve kalp krizine neden olabilir.\"]"
    source: "Ders kitab\u0131 s.132"
  - id: arteria_coronalis_dextra
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: vessel
    title: Arteria coronalis dextra
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Heart_External
    tags: heart; coronary; artery; right
    body: "Sa\u011F koroner arter (arteria coronalis dextra)"
    steps: " aorttan ayr\u0131lan ve kalbin sa\u011F taraf\u0131n\u0131 besleyen
      koroner damard\u0131r."
    source: "[\"Aorttan ayr\u0131lan ilk dallardan biridir.\", \"Kalp kas\u0131na
      oksijen ve besin bak\u0131m\u0131ndan zengin kan ta\u015F\u0131r.\"]"
  - id: arteria_coronalis_sinistra
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: vessel
    title: Arteria coronalis sinistra
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Heart_External
    tags: heart; coronary; artery; left
    body: Sol koroner arter (arteria coronalis sinistra)
    steps: " aorttan ayr\u0131lan ve kalbin sol taraf\u0131n\u0131 besleyen koroner
      damard\u0131r."
    source: "[\"Kalp kas\u0131n\u0131n b\xFCy\xFCk b\xF6l\xFCm\xFCne oksijen bak\u0131m\u0131ndan
      zengin kan ta\u015F\u0131r.\"]"
  - id: vena_cordis_magna
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: vessel
    title: Vena cordis magna
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Heart_External
    tags: heart; coronary; vein
    body: Vena cordis magna
    steps: " kalp kas\u0131ndan toplanan kirli kan\u0131 ta\u015F\u0131yan b\xFCy\xFCk
      koroner toplardamarlardan biridir."
    source: "[\"Bu damar kalbin y\xFCzeyindeki venlerle birle\u015Ferek koroner sin\xFCse
      kat\u0131l\u0131r.\"]"
  - id: vena_cordis_media
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: vessel
    title: Vena cordis media
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Heart_External
    tags: heart; coronary; vein
    body: Vena cordis media
    steps: " kalp kas\u0131ndan gelen kirli kan\u0131 toplayan koroner toplardamarlardan
      biridir."
    source: "[\"Bu damar da di\u011Fer koroner venlerle birlikte koroner sin\xFCse
      a\xE7\u0131l\u0131r.\"]"
  - id: vena_cordis_parva
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: vessel
    title: Vena cordis parva
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Heart_External
    tags: heart; coronary; vein
    body: Vena cordis parva
    steps: " kalp kas\u0131ndan gelen kirli kan\u0131 ta\u015F\u0131yan k\xFC\xE7\xFCk
      koroner toplardamarlardan biridir."
    source: "[\"Bu damar koroner venlerle birle\u015Ferek koroner sin\xFCse kat\u0131l\u0131r.\"]"
  - id: coronary_sinus
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: vessel
    title: Sinus coronarius
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Heart_External
    tags: heart; coronary; sinus
    body: Sinus coronarius
    steps: " kalp kas\u0131ndan gelen kirli kan\u0131n topland\u0131\u011F\u0131
      geni\u015F bir toplardamard\u0131r."
    source: "[\"Koroner venler burada birle\u015Fir ve kan buradan sa\u011F atriyuma
      d\xF6k\xFCl\xFCr.\"]"
  - id: cardiac_cycle
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: concept
    title: "Kalbin \xE7al\u0131\u015Fmas\u0131"
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Heart_Internal
    tags: heart; cardiac cycle; systole; diastole
    body: Kalp
    steps: " kendine ait uyar\u0131 \xE7\u0131karan h\xFCcreler sayesinde d\xFCzenli
      olarak kas\u0131l\u0131p gev\u015Fer."
    source: "[\"Kalbin kas\u0131lma evresine sistol, gev\u015Feme evresine ise diyastol
      denir.\" , \"Ventrik\xFCller kas\u0131ld\u0131\u011F\u0131nda kan atardamarlara
      pompalan\u0131r, gev\u015Fedi\u011Finde ise atriyumlardan gelen kan ventrik\xFCllere
      dolar.\" , \"Kapaklar kan\u0131n tek y\xF6nl\xFC ilerlemesini sa\u011Flar ve
      geri ka\xE7mas\u0131n\u0131 engeller.\"]"
  - id: tricuspid_valve
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: structure
    title: "Trik\xFCspit kapak"
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Heart_Internal
    tags: heart; valve; tricuspid
    body: "Trik\xFCspit kapak"
    steps: " sa\u011F kulak\xE7\u0131k ile sa\u011F kar\u0131nc\u0131k aras\u0131nda
      bulunan atriyoventrik\xFCler kapakt\u0131r."
    source: "[\"Ventrik\xFCl kas\u0131ld\u0131\u011F\u0131nda kan\u0131n tekrar kulak\xE7\u0131\u011Fa
      geri d\xF6nmesini engeller.\"]"
  - id: mitral_valve
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: structure
    title: Mitral kapak
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Heart_Internal
    tags: heart; valve; mitral
    body: Mitral kapak
    steps: " sol kulak\xE7\u0131k ile sol kar\u0131nc\u0131k aras\u0131nda bulunan
      atriyoventrik\xFCler kapakt\u0131r. "
    source: "[\"Kan\u0131n ventrik\xFCl kas\u0131lmas\u0131 s\u0131ras\u0131nda sol
      kulak\xE7\u0131\u011Fa geri ka\xE7mas\u0131n\u0131 engeller.\"]"
  - id: myocardium
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: structure
    title: Myocardium
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Heart_Internal
    tags: heart; muscle; myocardium
    body: Myokard
    steps: " kalbin kas\u0131lmas\u0131n\u0131 sa\u011Flayan kal\u0131n kas tabakas\u0131d\u0131r."
    source: "[\"Bu kas tabakas\u0131 kas\u0131larak kan\u0131n kalpten damarlara
      pompalanmas\u0131n\u0131 sa\u011Flar.\"]"
  - id: arteries
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: concept
    title: Atardamarlar
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Vessels
    tags: artery; arter; vessel; blood circulation; damar
    body: Atardamarlar
    steps: " kan\u0131 kalpten dokulara ve organlara ta\u015F\u0131yan kan damarlar\u0131d\u0131r."
    source: "[\"Atardamarlar kalbin ventrik\xFClleri ile ba\u011Flant\u0131l\u0131
      damarlard\u0131r ve kan\u0131 kalpten uzakla\u015Ft\u0131rarak v\xFCcudun farkl\u0131
      b\xF6lgelerine ta\u015F\u0131rlar.\", \"Sa\u011F ventrik\xFClden akci\u011Ferlere
      kirli kan ta\u015F\u0131yan akci\u011Fer atardamar\u0131 d\u0131\u015F\u0131nda
      di\u011Fer t\xFCm atardamarlar oksijen bak\u0131m\u0131ndan zengin temiz kan
      ta\u015F\u0131r.\", \"Sol ventrik\xFClden \xE7\u0131kan temiz kan sistol s\u0131ras\u0131nda
      aort damar\u0131na pompalan\u0131r ve buradan v\xFCcuttaki di\u011Fer atardamarlara
      da\u011F\u0131t\u0131l\u0131r.\", \"Atardamarlar\u0131n \xE7aplar\u0131 perifer
      b\xF6lgelere do\u011Fru gidildik\xE7e k\xFC\xE7\xFCl\xFCr ve bu k\xFC\xE7\xFCk
      damarlara arteriyol ad\u0131 verilir.\", \"Atardamarlarda kan bas\u0131nc\u0131
      y\xFCksek oldu\u011Fu i\xE7in damar duvarlar\u0131 toplardamarlara g\xF6re
      daha kal\u0131n ve dayan\u0131kl\u0131d\u0131r.\"]"
  - id: upper_extremity_arteries
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: concept
    title: "\xDCst ekstremite arterleri"
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Upper_Extremity
    tags: artery; arter; upper extremity; arm; kol; damar; subclavian; axillary;
      brachial; radial; ulnar
    body: "\xDCst ekstremite arterleri"
    steps: " omuzdan ele kadar \xFCst ekstremiteyi besleyen atardamarlard\u0131r."
    source: "[\"Sa\u011F ve sol k\xF6pr\xFCc\xFCk alt\u0131 arterleri kola do\u011Fru
      ilerledik\xE7e \xE7aplar\u0131 giderek k\xFC\xE7\xFCl\xFCr ve ge\xE7tikleri
      b\xF6lgeye g\xF6re farkl\u0131 isimler al\u0131rlar.\",\"\xDCst ekstremitede
      arterler s\u0131ras\u0131yla a. subclavia, a. axillaris, a. brachialis, a.
      radialis ve a. ulnaris olarak devam eder.\",\"Bu damarlar omuz, kol, \xF6n
      kol ve elin kanlanmas\u0131n\u0131 sa\u011Flar.\"]"
  - id: subclavian_artery
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: vessel
    title: A. subclavia
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Upper_Extremity
    tags: "artery; subclavian artery; a. subclavia; upper extremity; arter; k\xF6pr\xFCc\xFCk
      alt\u0131 atardamar\u0131; atardamar"
    body: A. subclavia
    steps: " \xFCst ekstremiteye kan ta\u015F\u0131yan ana arterlerden biridir."
    source: "[\"Sa\u011F ve sol a. subclavia, \xFCst ekstremiteye uzanan arteriyel
      dola\u015F\u0131m\u0131n ba\u015Flang\u0131\xE7 b\xF6l\xFCm\xFCn\xFC olu\u015Fturur.\",\"Bu
      damar kola do\u011Fru ilerledik\xE7e bulundu\u011Fu b\xF6lgeye g\xF6re isim
      de\u011Fi\u015Ftirir.\",\"Koltuk alt\u0131 b\xF6lgesine ula\u015Ft\u0131\u011F\u0131nda
      a. axillaris ad\u0131n\u0131 al\u0131r.\"]"
  - id: axillary_artery
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: vessel
    title: A. axillaris
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Upper_Extremity
    tags: "artery; arter; axillary artery; a. axillaris; koltuk alt\u0131 atardamar\u0131;
      upper extremity; atardamar"
    body: A. axillaris
    steps: " a. subclavia'n\u0131n koltuk alt\u0131 b\xF6lgesindeki devam\u0131d\u0131r."
    source: "[\"A. subclavia, koltuk alt\u0131 b\xF6lgesine geldi\u011Finde a. axillaris
