      aortu yakla\u015F\u0131k d\xF6rd\xFCnc\xFC bel omuru hizas\u0131nda ikiye ayr\u0131larak
      sa\u011F ve sol a. iliaca communis arterlerini olu\u015Fturur.\"]"
