  - id: veins
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: concept
    title: Toplardamarlar
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Vessels
    tags: vein; vena; ven; circulation; toplardamar
    body: Toplardamarlar
    steps: " kan\u0131 dokular ve akci\u011Ferlerden kalbe ta\u015F\u0131yan damar
      grubudur."
    source: "[\"Temiz kan\u0131 akci\u011Ferlerden kalbe ta\u015F\u0131yan akci\u011Fer
      toplardamarlar\u0131 d\u0131\u015F\u0131nda venler kirli kan ta\u015F\u0131r.\",\"Venlerde
      kan bas\u0131nc\u0131 arterlere g\xF6re daha d\xFC\u015F\xFCkt\xFCr.\",\"Ven
      duvarlar\u0131 arterlere g\xF6re daha incedir.\",\"Normal istirahat halinde
      dola\u015F\u0131mdaki kan\u0131n b\xFCy\xFCk bir b\xF6l\xFCm\xFC venlerde bulunur.\"]"
  - id: upper_extremity_veins
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: concept
    title: "\xDCst ekstremite venleri"
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Upper_Extremity
    tags: vein; upper extremity veins; arm veins; vena; toplardamar
    body: "\xDCst ekstremite venleri"
    steps: " kol b\xF6lgesindeki kirli kan\u0131 kalbe do\u011Fru ta\u015F\u0131yan
      toplardamarlard\u0131r."
    source: "[\"\xDCst ekstremite venleri y\xFCzeysel ve derin venler olmak \xFCzere
      iki grupta incelenir.\",\"Y\xFCzeysel venler deri alt\u0131nda seyreder ve
      g\xF6r\xFClebilir.\",\"\xD6nemli y\xFCzeysel venler aras\u0131nda v. cephalica,
      v. basilica, v. mediana antebrachii ve v. mediana cubiti bulunur.\",\"Derin
      venler arterlerle birlikte seyreder.\",\"\xD6nemli derin venler aras\u0131nda
      v. radialis, v. ulnaris, v. brachialis ve v. axillaris yer al\u0131r.\",\"\xDCst
      ekstremiteden gelen ven\xF6z kan v. subclavia \xFCzerinden daha b\xFCy\xFCk
      venlere ta\u015F\u0131n\u0131r.\"]"
  - id: brachiocephalica_vein
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: vessel
    title: V. brachiocephalica
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Upper_Extremity
    tags: vein; brachiocephalica; brachiocephalic vein; toplardamar
    body: V. brachiocephalica
    steps: " kol ve ba\u015F b\xF6lgesinden gelen venlerin birle\u015Fmesi ile olu\u015Fur."
    source: "[\"Ba\u015F b\xF6lgesinden gelen v. jugularis interna ile boynun d\u0131\u015F
      venlerinden v. jugularis externa birle\u015Fir.\",\"Koldan gelen v. subclavia
      ile birle\u015Ferek v. brachiocephalica olu\u015Fur.\"]"
  - id: jugularis_interna
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: vessel
    title: V. jugularis interna
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Neck
    tags: vein; jugularis interna; internal jugular vein; toplardamar
    body: "V. jugularis interna boyundaki en b\xFCy\xFCk vendir."
    steps: "[\"El s\u0131rt\u0131n\u0131n ulnar taraf\u0131ndan ba\u015Flar.\",\"\xD6n
      kolun i\xE7 y\xFCz\xFCnden yukar\u0131 do\u011Fru ilerler.\",\"Dirsek b\xF6lgesini
      ge\xE7erek kol b\xF6lgesine ula\u015F\u0131r.\",\"Kol b\xF6lgesinde derine
      ilerler ve derin ven\xF6z sistemle birle\u015Ferek v. axillaris'in olu\u015Fumuna
      kat\u0131l\u0131r.\"]"
    source: "Ders kitab\u0131 s.140"
  - id: jugularis_externa
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: vessel
    title: V. jugularis externa
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Neck
    tags: vein; jugularis externa; external jugular vein; toplardamar
    body: "V. jugularis externa ba\u015F\u0131n d\u0131\u015F venlerini ve y\xFCz\xFCn
      y\xFCzeysel venlerini toplar."
    steps: "[\"Ba\u015F ve y\xFCz\xFCn y\xFCzeysel venleri ile birle\u015Fir.\",\"Boyundan
      a\u015Fa\u011F\u0131 do\u011Fru ilerler.\",\"V. subclavia ile birle\u015Ferek
      sonlan\u0131r.\"]"
    source: "Ders kitab\u0131 s.140"
  - id: subclavia_vein
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: vessel
    title: V. subclavia
