    region: Upper_Extremity
    tags: vein; subclavia; subclavian vein; toplardamar
    body: V. subclavia
    steps: " v. axillaris'in k\xF6pr\xFCc\xFCk kemi\u011Fi alt\u0131ndaki devam\u0131
