  - id: lower_extremity_veins
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: concept
    title: Alt ekstremite venleri
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Lower_Extremity
    tags: vein; lower extremity veins; leg veins; vena; toplardamar
    body: "Alt ekstremite venleri bacak ve ayak b\xF6lgesindeki ven\xF6z kan\u0131
      kalbe do\u011Fru ta\u015F\u0131yan toplardamarlard\u0131r."
    steps: "[\"Alt ekstremite venleri y\xFCzeysel ve derin venler olmak \xFCzere
      iki grupta incelenir.\",\"Y\xFCzeysel venlerin yap\u0131s\u0131nda kapak\xE7\u0131klar
      bulunur.\",\"Derin venler genellikle ayn\u0131 isimdeki arterlerle birlikte
      seyreder.\",\"Alt ekstremiteden gelen ven\xF6z kan daha b\xFCy\xFCk venler
      arac\u0131l\u0131\u011F\u0131yla v. cava inferiora ta\u015F\u0131n\u0131r.\"]"
    source: "Ders kitab\u0131 s.141"
  - id: cava_inferior
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: vessel
    title: V. cava inferior
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Abdomen
    tags: vein; cava inferior; inferior vena cava; toplardamar
    body: "V. cava inferior g\xF6vdenin alt b\xF6l\xFCm\xFCnden gelen ven\xF6z kan\u0131
      kalbe ta\u015F\u0131yan b\xFCy\xFCk bir vendir."
    steps: "[\"G\xF6vdede diyafram\u0131n alt\u0131nda kalan b\xF6l\xFCm ile alt
      ekstremite b\xF6lgelerinin kan\u0131n\u0131 toplar.\",\"Sa\u011F ve sol v.
      iliaca communis'in birle\u015Fmesi ile olu\u015Fur.\",\"Toplad\u0131\u011F\u0131
      kan\u0131 kalbin sa\u011F atriumuna ta\u015F\u0131r.\"]"
    source: "Ders kitab\u0131 s.141"
  - id: iliaca_communis_vein
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: vessel
    title: V. iliaca communis
