  - id: systemic_circulation
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: concept
    title: "B\xFCy\xFCk kan dola\u015F\u0131m\u0131"
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Circulation
    tags: circulation; systemic; large_circulation; heart; body
    body: "B\xFCy\xFCk kan dola\u015F\u0131m\u0131"
    steps: " oksijen bak\u0131m\u0131ndan zengin kan\u0131n kalpten \xE7\u0131karak
      t\xFCm v\xFCcut dokular\u0131na g\xF6nderilmesini ve dokularda olu\u015Fan
      karbondioksit ile at\u0131k maddelerin toplanarak tekrar kalbe getirilmesini
      sa\u011Flayan dola\u015F\u0131md\u0131r."
    source: "[\"Oksijenlenmi\u015F kan pulmoner venler ile sol atriyuma gelir\",
      \"Kan mitral kapaktan ge\xE7erek sol ventrik\xFCle ula\u015F\u0131r\", \"Sol
      ventrik\xFCl kas\u0131larak kan\u0131 aort arac\u0131l\u0131\u011F\u0131yla
      t\xFCm v\xFCcuda pompalar\", \"Dokularda gaz de\u011Fi\u015Fimi ger\xE7ekle\u015Fir
      ve kan kirlenir\", \"Kirli kan vena cava damarlar\u0131 ile sa\u011F atriyuma
      geri d\xF6ner\"]"
  - id: pulmonary_circulation
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: concept
    title: "K\xFC\xE7\xFCk kan dola\u015F\u0131m\u0131"
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Circulation
    tags: circulation; pulmonary; small_circulation; heart; lung
    body: "K\xFC\xE7\xFCk kan dola\u015F\u0131m\u0131"
    steps: " kalpten akci\u011Ferlere g\xF6nderilen kirli kan\u0131n akci\u011Ferlerde
      oksijenlenerek temizlenmesi ve tekrar kalbe d\xF6nmesini sa\u011Flayan dola\u015F\u0131md\u0131r."
    source: "[\"Kirli kan sa\u011F atriyuma gelir\", \"Kan trik\xFCspit kapaktan
      ge\xE7erek sa\u011F ventrik\xFCle ula\u015F\u0131r\", \"Sa\u011F ventrik\xFCl
      kas\u0131larak kan\u0131 pulmoner arter arac\u0131l\u0131\u011F\u0131yla akci\u011Ferlere
      pompalar\", \"Akci\u011Ferlerde gaz de\u011Fi\u015Fimi ger\xE7ekle\u015Fir
      ve kan oksijenlenir\", \"Oksijenlenmi\u015F kan pulmoner venler ile sol atriyuma
      geri d\xF6ner\"]"
  - id: systemic_left_ventricle_01
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: structure
    title: "Sol ventrik\xFCl"
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Circulation
    tags: circulation; systemic; large_circulation; heart; ventricle
    body: "Sol ventrik\xFCl"
    steps: " oksijen bak\u0131m\u0131ndan zengin kan\u0131 aort arac\u0131l\u0131\u011F\u0131yla
      t\xFCm v\xFCcuda pompalayan ve b\xFCy\xFCk kan dola\u015F\u0131m\u0131n\u0131n
      ba\u015Flad\u0131\u011F\u0131 kalp odac\u0131\u011F\u0131d\u0131r."
    source: "[\"Sol atriyumdan gelen oksijenli kan sol ventrik\xFClde toplan\u0131r\",
      \"Ventrik\xFCl kas\u0131larak kan\u0131 kalpten d\u0131\u015Far\u0131 pompalar\",
      \"Kan aort damar\u0131na g\xF6nderilir\"]"
  - id: systemic_aorta_02
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: vessel
    title: Aort
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Circulation
    tags: circulation; systemic; large_circulation; vessel; artery; aorta
    body: Aort
    steps: " sol ventrik\xFClden pompalanan oksijen bak\u0131m\u0131ndan zengin kan\u0131
      t\xFCm v\xFCcuda da\u011F\u0131tan kalpten \xE7\u0131kan en b\xFCy\xFCk atardamard\u0131r."
    source: "[\"Sol ventrik\xFClden \xE7\u0131kan kan aort damar\u0131na ula\u015F\u0131r\",
      \"Aort \xE7e\u015Fitli dallara ayr\u0131larak kan\u0131 v\xFCcudun farkl\u0131
      b\xF6lgelerine ta\u015F\u0131r\"]"
  - id: systemic_body_arteries_03
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: vessel
    title: "V\xFCcut atardamarlar\u0131"
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Circulation
    tags: circulation; systemic; large_circulation; vessel; artery; systemic_artery
    body: "Aorttan ayr\u0131lan atardamarlar oksijen bak\u0131m\u0131ndan zengin
      kan\u0131 v\xFCcudun farkl\u0131 b\xF6lgelerindeki dokulara ta\u015F\u0131yan
      damarlard\u0131r."
    steps: "[\"Aorttan \xE7\u0131kan kan b\xFCy\xFCk atardamarlara ge\xE7er\", \"Atardamarlar
      dallanarak v\xFCcudun \xE7e\u015Fitli b\xF6lgelerine kan ta\u015F\u0131r\",
      \"Kan daha k\xFC\xE7\xFCk atardamarlara ve k\u0131lcal damarlara do\u011Fru
      ilerler\"]"
    source: "Ders kitab\u0131 s.145"
  - id: systemic_capillaries_04
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: vessel
    title: "V\xFCcut k\u0131lcal damarlar\u0131"
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Circulation
    tags: circulation; systemic; large_circulation; capillary; body
    body: "K\u0131lcal damarlar"
    steps: " kan ile h\xFCcreler aras\u0131nda gaz ve madde al\u0131\u015Fveri\u015Finin
      ger\xE7ekle\u015Fti\u011Fi en ince damarlard\u0131r."
    source: "[\"Oksijenli kan k\u0131lcal damarlara ula\u015F\u0131r\", \"H\xFCcreler
      oksijeni ve besin maddelerini al\u0131r\", \"Karbondioksit ve at\u0131k maddeler
      kana ge\xE7er\" , \"Kan kirli hale gelir\"]"
  - id: systemic_body_veins_05
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: vessel
    title: "V\xFCcut toplardamarlar\u0131"
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Circulation
    tags: circulation; systemic; large_circulation; vein; body
    body: Toplardamarlar
    steps: " dokularda gaz de\u011Fi\u015Fimi sonucu kirlenen kan\u0131 k\u0131lcal
      damarlardan alarak kalbe do\u011Fru ta\u015F\u0131yan damarlard\u0131r."
    source: "[\"K\u0131lcal damarlardan \xE7\u0131kan kirli kan k\xFC\xE7\xFCk toplardamarlara
      ge\xE7er\", \"Toplardamarlar birle\u015Ferek daha b\xFCy\xFCk damarlar\u0131
      olu\u015Fturur\", \"Kan kalbe do\u011Fru ta\u015F\u0131n\u0131r\"]"
  - id: systemic_vena_cava_06
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: vessel
    title: Vena cava
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Circulation
    tags: circulation; systemic; large_circulation; vein; vena_cava
    body: Vena cava superior ve vena cava inferior
    steps: " v\xFCcuttan gelen kirli kan\u0131 kalbin sa\u011F atriyumuna ta\u015F\u0131yan
      b\xFCy\xFCk toplardamarlard\u0131r."
    source: "[\"V\xFCcuttan gelen kirli kan b\xFCy\xFCk toplardamarlarda toplan\u0131r\",
      \"Kan vena cava damarlar\u0131na ula\u015F\u0131r\", \"Vena cava kan\u0131
      kalbin sa\u011F atriyumuna ta\u015F\u0131r\"]"
  - id: systemic_right_atrium_07
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: structure
    title: "Sa\u011F atriyum"
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Circulation
    tags: circulation; systemic; large_circulation; heart; atrium
    body: "Sa\u011F atriyum"
    steps: " vena cava damarlar\u0131 arac\u0131l\u0131\u011F\u0131yla v\xFCcuttan
      gelen kirli kan\u0131n topland\u0131\u011F\u0131 kalp odac\u0131\u011F\u0131d\u0131r."
    source: "[\"Vena cava damarlar\u0131ndan gelen kan sa\u011F atriyuma ula\u015F\u0131r\",
      \"Sa\u011F atriyum kan\u0131 sa\u011F ventrik\xFCle iletmeye haz\u0131r hale
      getirir\"]"
  - id: pulmonary_right_ventricle_01
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: structure
    title: "Sa\u011F ventrik\xFCl"
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Circulation
    tags: circulation; pulmonary; small_circulation; heart; ventricle; right_ventricle
    body: "Sa\u011F ventrik\xFCl"
    steps: " kirli kan\u0131 pulmoner arter arac\u0131l\u0131\u011F\u0131yla akci\u011Ferlere
      pompalayan kalp odac\u0131\u011F\u0131d\u0131r."
    source: "[\"Sa\u011F atriyumdan gelen kirli kan sa\u011F ventrik\xFClde toplan\u0131r\",
      \"Sa\u011F ventrik\xFCl kas\u0131l\u0131r\", \"Kan pulmoner artere pompalan\u0131r\"]"
  - id: pulmonary_artery_02
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: vessel
    title: Pulmoner arter (A. pulmonalis)
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Circulation
    tags: circulation; pulmonary; small_circulation; vessel; artery; pulmonary_artery
    body: Pulmoner arter
    steps: " kirli kan\u0131 kalpten akci\u011Ferlere ta\u015F\u0131yan atardamard\u0131r."
    source: "[\"Sa\u011F ventrik\xFClden \xE7\u0131kan kirli kan pulmoner artere
      ula\u015F\u0131r\", \"Pulmoner arter kan\u0131 akci\u011Ferlere ta\u015F\u0131r\",
      \"Kan akci\u011Fer k\u0131lcal damarlar\u0131na do\u011Fru ilerler\"]"
  - id: pulmonary_capillaries_03
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: vessel
    title: "Akci\u011Fer k\u0131lcal damarlar\u0131"
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Circulation
    tags: circulation; pulmonary; small_circulation; vessel; capillary; lung_capillary
    body: "Akci\u011Fer k\u0131lcal damarlar\u0131"
    steps: " kan ile alveoller aras\u0131nda gaz de\u011Fi\u015Fiminin ger\xE7ekle\u015Fti\u011Fi
      damarlard\u0131r."
    source: "[\"Kirli kan akci\u011Fer k\u0131lcal damarlar\u0131na ula\u015F\u0131r\",
      \"Karbondioksit alveollere verilir\", \"Oksijen kana ge\xE7er\", \"Kan oksijen
      bak\u0131m\u0131ndan zengin hale gelir\"]"
  - id: pulmonary_vein_04
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: vessel
    title: Pulmoner ven (V. pulmonalis)
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Circulation
    tags: circulation; pulmonary; small_circulation; vessel; vein; pulmonary_vein
    body: Pulmoner ven
    steps: " akci\u011Ferlerde oksijenlenen kan\u0131 kalbe ta\u015F\u0131yan toplardamard\u0131r."
    source: "[\"Akci\u011Ferlerde oksijenlenen kan pulmoner venlere ge\xE7er\", \"Pulmoner
      venler kan\u0131 kalbe ta\u015F\u0131r\", \"Kan sol atriyuma ula\u015F\u0131r\"]"
  - id: pulmonary_left_atrium_05
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: structure
    title: Sol atriyum
    topic: Circulatory System
    region: Circulation
    tags: circulation; pulmonary; small_circulation; heart; atrium; left_atrium
    body: Sol atriyum
    steps: " akci\u011Ferlerden gelen oksijen bak\u0131m\u0131ndan zengin kan\u0131n
